{"tid":738603,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"啱啱幫港鐵廣告配音","createTime":"2018-07-11T15:45:22.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-11T15:45:22.000Z","uid":190472,"like":0,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"6e3861996505c8130f5a0e9daaaa364bd04b0a06","tid":738603,"uid":190472,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-11T15:45:22.000Z","msg":"老實講成個樣真係好似 &quot;你的名字&quot;<br />\n我重諗緊佢會唔會被人告<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/02.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n雖然我撐香港自家人嘅出品<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n如果有香港情意結  當然都希望香港人某方面有進步同出色(可惜係抄人嘅)<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同埋我都希望佢抄完之後  會去嘗試搵返自己嘅風格<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n不過講到尾  對方單係港鐵呢一點<br />\n想撐都撐唔落手  因為本身間公司都食緊屎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n然後我純粹覺得佢D配音一般  想去試改下<br />\n玩玩下就搞咗條咁嘅野出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n如果大家有浦開網絡嘅話  應該會發現到一兩個聲音來源嘅出處<br />\n睇下你地識得幾多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好笑就好，唔好笑就比個dislike<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n等我知邊個位唔好<br />\n<br />\n今次無寫犒就講野  LAG到我自己都尷尬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n重有大家知唔知佢會唔會出第二集?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Zg__H_flloQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DZg__H_flloQ&d=EvadK5HR1ZLTZEmuU2f4FDCdMQr7etzq9tFbjrA%2B72k%3D&h=f24601c0\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Zg__H_flloQ</a>"}]}